\CE[79]\CE[84]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>You've come. I suppose your determination has
solidified.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>What's wrong? I want to hear it from your own
mouth. Why did you come here? What do you want?
D_TEXT (\C[27]バスタに抱かれる\C[0]のか、\C[1]ジャスに操を立てる\C[0]のか……！？ 32

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>...............Pleas e tell me the location of the
underground club with the magic device............

\CE[94]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>────............Plea se do as you please with my
body......

\CE[94]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>No matter how much I offer my body... my heart is
still thinking of someone important...!

\CE[94]\CE[79]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Someone important? Hehehehe... Well, I suppose
that's fine.

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Instead... please make sure to tell me how to get
to the club!

\OC[6]\N<Buster>I understand. I'll keep that promise. But before
that, I'm going to have a lot of fun with you.

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>H-Here!? In a place like this... where other
people... are doing it...

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Don't worry about it, this is that kind of place.
There's no need to be concerned. Aren't you
looking around at everyone else too?

\CE[79]\CE[78]\OC[31]\N<Rain>In a place like this... is there really no other
place where there are no people's eyes...?

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Shut up, just do it quietly and take off your
clothes before I change my mind.
\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Or should we stop if you don't want to do it here?

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Alright, good girl. Now, come on, hurry up and get
on top.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>Don't think you can just stay silent and be
fucked. You're going to be fucked of your own
will. Prove it.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>You're quite a mess, Rain. Was it that good?
Hehehe...

\CE[79]\CE[78]\CE[83]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>───... ......I absolutely refuse to be embraced by
you!

\CE[79]\CE[83]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>...Oh? So that means you don't need any
information, huh?

\OC[6]\N<Buster>So, because you value your own safety so much,
you're willing to sacrifice the townspeople and
take your time searching for the device, right?

\CE[78]\CE[83]\CE[84]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>No, that's not it. I'm saying that even if I have
to beat you down, I will definitely make you talk!

\OC[31]\N<Rain>I have someone important to me. For that person's
sake, I won't stoop to selling myself to malicious
individuals! Instead, I will do whatever it takes
to accomplish my goal!

\OC[31]\N<Rain>I will never become yours! Neither my heart nor my
body...!

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>...Is that your answer? Fine then. Just so you
know, it won't be so easy to find the club. The
underground of this town is much darker than you
think.

\CE[94]\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>...Yes, I am prepared. However, my... as a holy
knight, my body is not cheap!

\CE[79]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Now, you will be locked up in a cell! If I don't
catch you off guard, 'Nightmare Heaven' won't work
on me. Prepare yourself!
\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Fine, fine. I get it, I get it. I admit defeat.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>Well, I can't help it if you're going to refuse me
that much. I'll back off for now. But I don't want
to end up in a cell either. I'll tell you how to
get to the club!

\CE[79]\CE[78]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>You seem quite willing to give up,
\....\....\....\..

\CE[79]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Hmph, I don't have time to dilly-dally with
someone who has clearly rejected me up until now.
It's obvious that we should get to the point
quickly.
\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>So, the way to the underground club, huh.

\CE[79]\CE[78]\CE[84]\CE[83]\OC[31]\N<Rain>Of course, that's important, but before that, what
exactly is this 'club'? And why are there magical
devices there..........

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>What, there's one in every town, like a gathering
place for delinquents.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Drinking, making noise, doing drugs, getting high,
and having sex. It's a vulgar place that doesn't
suit someone as refined as you.

\CE[84]\CE[83]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Have you seen the underground passages in this
town? They've been taken over by vagrants and
turned into a filthy cesspool that would make
anyone on the surface cringe. I don't know who did
it, but it seems like someone saw potential in
that place and created it.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>Even though it's a place that no one pays
attention to, it's a gathering spot for criminals.
It's not easy to find or enter in case of
emergencies. It's just the perfect place to hide
something.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>So, you're trying to stick your foot into that
filthy cesspool, huh? \.Well, what do you say? Are
you still going to quit?

\CE[94]\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[83]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain> Being a knight is not something so lukewarm that
you would interrupt a mission for such trivial
matters.

\OC[31]\N<Rain>And if criminals are gathering there, then all the
more reason to go...!

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>As for the crucial location, \C[17] come to the
cheap inn in the underground passage during the
day \C[0]. I'll guide you from there.

\CE[79]\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Ah, I get it, I get it. You're worried that I
might run away, right?

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>But unless I personally introduce you, you won't
be able to get in. You heard it earlier, right?
It's not that easy to get in. There's no helping
it.

\CE[94]\OC[6]\N<Buster>If you're worried about me running away, how about
sleeping with me tonight? Well, of course, I won't
be able to sleep quietly.

\CE[78]\CE[79]\CE[84]\OC[31]\N<Rain>.........Unde rstood. In front of the cheap inn
during the day, starting from tomorrow.

\CE[79]\OC[6]\N<Buster>Well, whatever. If you understand, then just go
already. Having a stick- in-the-mud like you
around ruins the adult atmosphere here.
心メーターで理性を選んだ場合のみの演出

\OC[6]\N<Buster>(───I was planning to settle things this time,
but... well, whatever. It's actually convenient if
you can take me to that place.

\OC[6]\N<Buster>(Sorry, Rain. I'm going to be forceful with you...
hehe...)
心メーターで欲望を選んだ場合のみの演出

\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(─────.........I...did it..........with someone
other than Jazz..........

\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(But, this... is for the mission... I only put my
body on the line for the mission...)

\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(My heart... my heart has always been thinking of
Jazz... \. That's why... \.... \.... \. I'm
sorry...)

\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(I can't undo what I've done. I need to switch
gears...!)

\OC[31]\N<Inner Rain>(Since I put my body on the line, I'll show you
that I can recover that much...!)
